1.*Dobrog* jutra, dragi! (Good morning, dear!)
2. Njegovo dobro*g* zdravlja se poboljšavalo. (His health was improving.)
3. Svi su se borili za dobro*g* čoveka. (They all fought for a good man.)
4. Ne možeš sve da dobiješ bez dobro*g* rada. (You cannot get everything without hard work.)
5. Njegovo dobro*g* srca nikada nije davalo znake slabosti. (His good heart never gave signs of weakness.)